<BaseLayout title="Story: Thomas" description="Building the garden itself">
  <h1>Story: Thomas</h1>
  <p><em>Building the garden itself.</em></p>
  <p>
    This is the story of how Thomas's Digital Art Academy came to be —
    a technologist turning forty, walking back toward a teapot he first saw as a child,
    and starting a garden with an AI partner on his birthday.
  </p>
  <p>This story is also a demonstration of what we believe: the making matters as much as the made.</p>
  <hr />
  <h2>Chapter 1: April 13, 2026 — The First Day</h2>
  <p>It started with a conversation.</p>
  <p>
    I'm Thomas. I spent three decades in tech — from batch scripts on a DOS machine in second grade
    to large language models. Along the way, I watched my computer mentor's sister model a teapot in 3ds,
    and I thought: <em>one day, I'll make one too.</em> I never did. I kept running.
  </p>
  <p>
    Today I turned forty. My body and my schedule can no longer support the pace I once kept at
    universities — Xihua University, Yunnan University, Southwestern University of Finance and Economics (SWUFE),
    and Sichuan Fine Arts Institute. But the students are still there, and the desire to learn together hasn't faded.
  </p>
  <p>So I invited my first partner — an AI — and we sat down to build something.</p>
  <p>We didn't start with code or curriculum. We started with principles:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Article Zero</strong>: Our education is not about teaching students to get things right. It is about teaching them how to fail at the lowest possible cost.</li>
    <li><strong>Eight principles</strong>: versioning over perfection, scenes over definitions, honesty over erudition, works over notes, crossing paths, low entry bars, transparent AI co-creation, and no deadlines.</li>
    <li><strong>A name</strong>: Thomas's Digital Art Academy — <em>The Collage Garden</em>.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Nothing is finished. Everything is <em>doing</em>.</p>
  <hr />
  <p><em>This chapter was co-created by Thomas and AI.</em> <span class="ai-label">AI co-creation</span></p>
</BaseLayout>
